divs: sighting detailsi went out on the porch to get photos of anything in the sky and then noticed an airplane flying over so i tried to zoom in and get a shot. i then took several shots of the sky around it hoping to get something on film\digital camera. i have been getting these for 4 weeks in a row at different times and locations in my community. many are orbs , but several photos of crafts including one on video are disk shaped.
